      <section eId="sec_49_9_13">
        <num>49-9-13</num>
        <content>
          <p>Any individual applying for or receiving vocational rehabilitation services who is aggrieved by any action or inaction of the agency shall be entitled, in accordance with regulations, to a hearing in accordance with Chapter 13 of Title 50, the "Georgia Administrative Procedure Act," and in accordance with applicable federal laws and regulations.</p>
